<!-- CSS variables, or custom properties, are placeholders for values you want to reuse in your stylesheets.





Example=====>>>>
(Agr hume same colour apni file m kai jgh chahiye to use baar baar likhne ki vajh hum css variable use kr skte h)

:root {
  --primary-color: #007bff;
}

button {
  background-color: var(--primary-color);
  color: white;
}




SYNTAX====> Variables start with -- (double hyphen) followed by a name. */
